Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.49,0:23:44.16,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,探險！發現！遊樂設施！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.16,0:23:46.49,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,今天要介紹的是「奶油古董店」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:48.45,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,等一下 這是最後一回了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:50.25,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,還有這個「NO IMAGE」是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:51.46,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:54.33,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,「奶油古董店」充滿夢想的商店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:56.13,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,大家都喜歡的「奶油古董店」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:57.54,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,不用重複那麼多遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:59.59,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,大家都來的「奶油古董店」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.59,0:24:02.42,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,哦 是什麼宣傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:05.01,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,嗯 請多關照「奶油古董店」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:07.43,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,雖然我也不知道是什麼商店
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:09.52,zhengwen-sommio,,0,0,0,,你去了解一下啊！
